# Agent Rules System — 340B Dashboard

When working on print, PDF, map visibility, or improvement prompts:

1. **Meta rules:** [AGENT-RULES-SYSTEM.md](AGENT-RULES-SYSTEM.md) — stability rules, update workflow, release gate.
2. **50 improvements:** [AGENT-TEMPLATE.md](AGENT-TEMPLATE.md) — batches A–E.
3. **Print/PDF:** Preserve `hap340bPrint` flow; map must be visible in both print view and Download PDF (image).
4. **Do not:** Add overflow:hidden to map-wrap; change scroll-reveal logic; put PDF CSS in 340b.css.
